OL,5, Money borrowed to pay for Christmas    
OL,6, could take years to repay, a charity   
OL,7, has warned, as a poll for the BBC      
OL,8, reflects fears over unmanageable debt. 
OL,10,FA third of respondents who used credit 
OL,11,Fto help get through Christmas and the  
OL,12,Fholiday season said they were not      
OL,13,Fconfident about their ability to repay.
OL,15,FAdvice charity StepChange said a debt  
OL,16,Fhangover led to a surge in enquiries.  
OL,18,FIt advised more people on 3 January,   
OL,19,Fthe first working day after the festive
OL,20,Fbreak, than on any day last year.      
